Today is International Day for the Elimination of Violence against Women. This is an UN campaign to stop violence against women! #orangetheworld 
I‚Äòm reposting this banner I made for #powerfulwomenweek to spread awareness to this topic. Swipe to see the whole picture. 
Violence against women is happening all around the world, to women of every age. It‚Äòs the most common violation of human rights. 
Even here where I live, in such a small country like Austria, had been 41 murders of women in 2018. 
Stand up for those who can not stand up anymore. Be aware in daily life, talk about it, support each other. 
I‚Äòm sure every women has at least one story were she was a victim of sexual harassment. .
